{"tid":1589623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣【 9.28 + 10.1 】連發宣傳","createTime":"2019-09-23T11:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T06:33:33.000Z","uid":173916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9719823a3c074a1844deae87dd775525d3ccd6","tid":1589623,"uid":173916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:05:21.000Z","msg":"五年前的9月28日，催淚彈劃破夏愨道的半空，開展一場劍指真普選的佔領運動。<br />\n<br />\n五年過去，真普選雖仍遙遙無期，而警察比以前更黑、更暴力、更不受監管。但是，香港人履行了在當日佔領結束時許下的承諾 －「人民誓將歸來」。五年後的香港人，以更團結、更鏗鏘、更堅毅的姿態再次站到政權的面前，對抗警暴，爭取雙真普選。<br />\n<br />\n9月28日，作為一個我們都記得；我們都認為是重要的日子 － 雨傘運動五周年，我們希望和大家一同回到金鐘，在集會當中沉澱、思考。<br />\n<br />\n同時，縱然當前要舉辦一個合法的遊行是會被多番刁難，而部份手足亦已經視不反對通知書為廢紙，但我們仍入紙希望可以舉辦10.1遊行，盡力讓當日能夠有一個讓所有香港人都能夠參與的大遊行，因此約定大家，十月一日，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【 9.28 反抗威權 迎接黎明 】集會<br />\n2019年9月28日<br />\n晚上7時至9時<br />\n金鐘添馬公園<br />\n<br />\n【 10.1 沒有國慶 只有國殤 】遊行<br />\n2019年10月1日<br />\n下午兩時起步<br />\n維園集合，遊行往遮打道<br />\n<br />\n主辦︰民間人權陣線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8BWutbg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8BWutbg.jpg&h=806fa2ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba1e0e7376a308a1b7a4db640fc22f51efa5ea35","tid":1589623,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:06:53.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[一至五帶風向]教大家phone-in節目提高駁入直播室嘅成功率<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74baeb61fdd56e0d0eccf52b6e6f38688d8ceed8","tid":1589623,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[一至五帶風向]教大家phone-in節目提高駁入直播室嘅成功率<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9b825af844458efdcffb0b14ed9c653a4c5b9cea","tid":1589623,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"a49faac3caf5430f43908f01cf4ce2c1b216b73b","tid":1589623,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858d510c454285951de60464c475196156bd970d","tid":1589623,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">十月一 &middot; 港九新界加機場 遍地開花 封哂成個香港丫笨</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">10.1全民黑衫果褲舉黑遮大集會，再放手放開所有咁放黑汽球上天</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fd1df6c7c3a310cbfe1a408fa7550cb867ff2db5","tid":1589623,"uid":52985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:53:20.000Z","msg":"個個提928 101咁929呢？<br />\n仲係咪要出<br />\n我覺得929比任何一日都重要<br />\n係全球首次同一目標對抗中共既日子"},{"pid":"6bac54ee2a3813028415b7497f13069fb8919527","tid":1589623,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:54:02.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"45f7475233061d55dbdffdecc794fab8008af651","tid":1589623,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea12819336f8737c4558aa1647feff6d5d910e14","tid":1589623,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum